## üîß Development

### Setting up the Environment

```bash
git clone https://github.com/SikamikanikoBG/codelens.git
cd codelens
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### Running Tests

```bash
pytest
```

